snippet.title: Into the Realm: Turn based RPG Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the Realm and fight orcs, goblins, men, elves, trolls, dragons and many more different foes!
Engage in tactical turn based combat using melee weapons, bows and offensive or defensive magic!
